  title="Hardwood Flooring in Houston's Humidity: What Actually Works | Jamail Hardwoods"
  description="Houston's humidity is the #1 cause of hardwood floor failures. Here's what works, what fails, and how to specify a floor that survives 30+ years."
>
  <Header />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
